org.webcat.deveventtracker.models.metrics

Class EarlyOften

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.webcat.deveventtracker.models.metrics.EarlyOften

  • public class EarlyOften
extends Object
    Handles calculation of the Early/Often index and storage of intermediate states for it. The Early/Often index is a quantification of procrastination on a software project.
    Version:
    2018-09-13
    Author:
    Ayaan Kazerouni
